The paper deals with understanding the intermediate representations captured by deep networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the mapping of semantic concepts to vectorial embeddings, which is related to natural language processing (cs.CL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with the behavior of filters in neural networks, which is a topic in neural networks (cs.NE).
